class Solution {
 public:
  int flipLights(int n, int m) {
    if (n == 0) return 0;
    if (n >= 1 && m == 0) return 1;
    if (n == 1)
      return 2;
    else if (n == 2 && m == 1)
      return 3;
    else if (n == 2 && m > 1)
      return 4;
    else if (n >= 3 && m == 1)
      return 4;
    else if (n >= 3 && m == 2)
      return 7;
    else
      return 8;
  }
};
```
### The idea is :
* Every even Flips will cancel each other out
* Every Flips 1 = Flips 2 + Flips 3
* When n < 3  Flips 3 = Flips 4  
### So there are only 8 condition:
* even Flips 4
* even Flips 4 + Flips 1
* even Flips 4 + Flips 2
