Most solutions in Leetcode have really non descriptive variable names which makes it tough to figure out what is happening (although granted everyone writing those solutions is absolutely brilliant, and I'm also nearly always guilty of this in LC). But after finishing the algorithm this time I rewrote it with proper variable naming so that if anyone does come across this post, there's hopefully more clarity provided in the different relationships between variables and how the logic comes into place.

